<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../partials/new-head', { title: 'Kidamame Discovery | The Calm App for Kids' ,
  url: 'https://www.kidamame.com/discovery.html' }) %>

  <body>
    <%- include('../partials/new-nav', { alwaysScrolled: true, hideNavItems: false }) %>

      <main style="padding-top: 100px; background: var(--white);">
        <!-- PRODUCT -->
        <section class="product" id="apps" style="padding-top: 4rem;">
          <div class="container">
            <p class="section-label reveal"><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen"></i> &nbsp;Our App</p>
            <h2 class="section-title reveal">Kidamame <em>Discovery</em></h2>

            <div class="product-simple-content reveal">
              <p>
                Welcome to a calm, interactive world designed for families. <strong>Kidamame Discovery</strong> replaces
                fast-paced goals and instructions with <strong>child-led exploration</strong>, inviting kids to touch,
                play, and learn at their own pace.
              </p>

              <div class="simple-gallery">
                <img src="images/gallery/thumbs/kidamame_discovery_home.webp" class="landscape"
                  alt="A wildlife educational app screenshot in the Alps." loading="lazy" />
              </div>

              <h3
                style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--ink);">
                Pure Exploration & Wonder</h3>
              <p>
                Built entirely around curiosity, there are absolutely <strong>no things to win and no puzzles to
                  solve</strong>. Kids simply pan across the landscape, explore the environment, and listen to the
                authentic sounds of animals and nature. Tapping the magnifying glass reveals beautifully illustrated
                cards filled with fascinating facts about each element.
              </p>

              <div class="simple-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
                <img src="images/gallery/thumbs/artic.webp" class="landscape"
                  alt="A wildlife educational app screenshot in the Artic featuring a polar bear with its cub"
                  loading="lazy" />
                <img src="images/gallery/thumbs/11.webp" class="landscape"
                  alt="A wildlife educational app screenshot in the African Savannah with mount Kilimanjaro"
                  loading="lazy" />
              </div>

              <h3
                style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--ink);">
                Interactive Secrets & Surprises</h3>
              <p>
                Every sensory-rich scene contains about <strong>20 interactive elements</strong> and hidden surprises.
                We focus on the "small wonders," showing how even the tiniest creatures or plants hide big secrets. Tap
                the ostrich to see its eggs fall, touch the volcano to trigger a spectacular eruption, or watch the
                glacier front collapse into the sea!
              </p>

              <div class="simple-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
                <img src="images/gallery/thumbs/13.webp" class="landscape"
                  alt="A wildlife educational app screenshot in the Australian Red Center with Uluru and a kangaroo"
                  loading="lazy" />
                <img src="images/gallery/thumbs/amazon_forest_2.webp" class="landscape"
                  alt="A wildlife educational app screenshot in the Amazon forest featuring a tucan and a macaw parrot"
                  loading="lazy" />
              </div>

              <h3
                style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--ink);">
                A Growing World</h3>
              <p>
                The app features <strong>6 stunning scenes</strong>, including the Alps, the African Savannah, the
                Australian Outback, the Arctic, and the Amazon Rainforest. With around 120 interactive elements and 3
                fun facts per element, there are <strong>over 400 interesting facts</strong> waiting to be discovered!
              </p>

              <div class="simple-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
                <img src="images/gallery/thumbs/05.webp" class="landscape"
                  alt="A wildlife educational app screenshot in the Australian Red Center with Uluru and a kangaroo"
                  loading="lazy" />
              </div>

              <h3
                style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--ink);">
                Quality Time Together</h3>
              <p>
                We designed Kidamame Discovery as a shared experience. The app shines when a child plays alongside an
                adult, exploring the biomes together while the parent helps reading the fun facts which, by the way, are
                genuinely interesting for adults too! Our ultimate aspiration is that this shared digital wonder will
                inspire your family to step outside and discover the magic of the real world.
              </p>

              <div class="simple-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
                <img src="images/gallery/thumbs/01.webp" class="landscape"
                  alt="A parent and child exploring nature together with Kidamame Discovery app" loading="lazy" />
              </div>

              <div class="reveal"
                style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3.5rem; background: var(--blue-light); padding: 2.5rem 2rem; border-radius: 20px;">
                <h4
                  style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 0.8rem;">
                  Stay in the loop!
                </h4>
                <p
                  style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Want to be the first to know when <strong>Kidamame Discovery</strong> launches on the Google Play
                  Store and the Apple App Store? Sign
                  up
                  to our newsletter for updates, behind-the-scenes content, and early access opportunities!
                </p>
                <a href="https://kidamame.substack.com/subscribe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="btn-primary">
                  ✨ Join our newsletter
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <%- include('../partials/new-footer') %>
  </body>

</html>